One time Nollywood Actress-turned entrepreneur, Carolyna Hutchings has confessed to her love for luxury and the good things of life. Carolyna made the confession during a tete-a-tete with Toyin Lawani, Iyabo Ojo, Chioma Ikoku, three of the characters of the Real Housewives of Lagos.   Ex-Miss World Uganda launches foundation to keep girls in…     Marriage? Count me out, says Iyabo Ojo     Teni Makanaki thrills at Gbenga Adeyinka’s Laffmattazz show   In one of the recent episodes of the show, Carolyna opined that she can’t date nor marry a man, who isn’t financially stable. She stressed her preference for wealthy men and possibly a billionaire. However, the beautiful mother of one, who was once married to a Nigerian billionaire, said not many people would believe that she wasn’t happy while in the marriage. She claimed that after getting into the life of a billionaire’s wife, many things weren’t making her happy, hence, the need to quit the marriage. Carolyna also disclosed she’s seeing another man but would not reveal the identity.